===Verb===
'''켜다''' (kyeoda)

# To [[turn on]] (switch), [[light]] (lamp, candle), [[strike]] (match) 
# To [[gulp]] (drinks) 
# To [[cut]] (as with the saw)  cf. Latin [[caedere]]
# To [[play]] the violin or the like

